author: Nexcell Pride
text:
About 4 hours of full fun... :_ちょうちょ:
This not only marks Rushia's return to Minecraft after almost 1 Month without playing or making adventures, also marks the first time playing Minecraft within New PC (Notorious for Prototype Opening and non defined BGM)

Talking about non defined BGM, at least Rushia's good tastes at music makes more interesting the stream.

And about running Minecraft at New PC makes a great difference, Speed and Aiming were too improving. :_きゅん:
Rushia didn't improve the Shading (A mode within Lights and Shadow are more detailed at objects)

Something... How did she recover the "Tsurupettachi Kai"? She lost it about 1 Month ago during a failed mission about obtaining Creeper's head. 

The adventure was about travelling various worlds using the Elytra and fireworks for make impulse. Founding various Villages for obtaining various items and burning fortress, along with gaining experience. Additionally, Rushia made various surviving operations, the same as Minecraft Hardcore of 2020 September 17th. :_るんるん:

One of the best parts was the 1:24:03, meanwhile Rushia was laughing maniacally, found the form of making pillagers killing themselves, also she was shooting against them. :_くさｗ:

At 1:52:33, bee found... Moment for capture it and carrying into the honeycomb harvest

Other things didn't changed, like... The automatic Sugar cane harvest. :_ハート:

Interesting note: at mid stream, Rushia did notice about Kaigainiki (Overseas viewers) and about hour during stream... Like... At Miami Florida, Argentina and Chile, stream started about 11:30 a.m. and ended totally about 3:30 p.m.

And the Supaachaato Orei Time was too accidented... Between YouTube being Guruguru and Rushia being attacked by Nyanko-Sensei.

Personal Marks: 3:20:47 (During "Taiki Nanodesu") and 3:51:55 (Message already read by Rushia) :_ハート: :_サイリウム碧: :_サイリウム紫: :_きゅん:
